@AdherenceService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5105

### Retrieve adherence records for a specific user
GET {{AdherenceService_HostAddress}}/adherence/user/user123
Accept: application/json

###

### Trigger an adherence alert for a specific record
POST {{AdherenceService_HostAddress}}/adherence/alert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "medicationId": "med456",
  "scheduledDoseTime": "2025-03-08T08:00:00Z",
  "actualDoseTime": null,
  "isDoseTaken": false,
  "alertTriggered": false,
  "note": "Dose missed, please check."
}

###
